    <stitle>TSI 06-12-07R - Redesigned Front Covers</stitle>
    <tsi id="tSI061207R" year="2006" tsitype="engine">
        <tsinumber>06-12-07R</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>November 2006</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>Engine</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Redesigned Front Covers</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <engfamgroup/>

                <engfam>DT 466</engfam>
                <engfam>DT 570</engfam>
                <engfam>HT 570</engfam>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>This TSI replaces 06-12-07.</para>
                <para>This updated TSI adds another new serviceable front half front cover.</para>
                <para>Redesigned front covers (front and rear halves) are used on both standard and Power Takeoff (PTO)
                    applications. These covers apply to all engines starting with serial number 2000001 and up. The
                    redesigned covers have resulted in the removal of the sound dampening shield assembly. Additional
                    changes include the following:
                </para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>Elimination of the water pump wear plate from the new front cover design (rear half) and
                            from all service kits.
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>The addition of three M8 x 50 thru bolts, nuts, and four O-rings.</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>A special Thredseal&#174; assembly was also added.</para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Whenever a front cover utilizing a Thredseal is removed, a new Thredseal assembly must be
                            used during reassembly.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <para>Another new front cover (front half) part number 1876912C1, has been released to replace the front
                    cover (front half) on engines with serial numbers ranging from 2000001 through 2102568.
                </para>
                <para>See Table 3 for serviceability effects.</para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
